title: Add customer/Compliance with the mockup
preconditions: Open https://demo.guru99.com/telecom/addcustomer.php
steps_actions:
1. There is a logo in the header of the page
2. There is a name of the page "Add Customer" below the logo
3. There is a header " Background Check "
4. There are 2 radio buttons "Done" and "Pending"
5. There is a header " Billing address"
6. There are 5 text fields with the name and placeholder which repeats its name
7. There is a button SUBMIT
8. There is a button RESET
9. There is a Hamburger menu button
steps_result:
1. Logo in the header of the page is present
2. The name of the page "Add Customer" below the logo is present
3. Header "Background Check" is present
4. Radio buttons "Done" and "Pending" are present
5. Header "Billing address" is present
6. 5 fields with placeholder are present
7. SUBMIT button is present
8. RESET button is present
9. Hamburger menu is present
steps_data:
1. 
2. 
3. 
4. 
5. 
6. FirstName, LastName, Email, Enter your address, Mobile Number
7. 
8. 
9.

steps_actions: 1. Click on the Logo sign in the page header
steps_result: 1. Redirected to Main Page

title: Add customer/Hamburger menu design and actions
preconditions:
1. Open https://demo.guru99.com/telecom/addcustomer.php
2. Open Hamburger Menu
steps_actions:
1. Click outside the hamburger menu
2. Click on the Hamburger menu button
3. Click on X button
4. Click on the Hamburger menu button
5. Check that there are 5 buttons
6. Click on any button except X
steps_result:
1. Hamburger menu is closed
2. Hamburger menu opens
3. Hamburger menu is closed
4. Hamburger menu is open
5. There are 5 buttons
6. Redirected to button destination
steps_data:
1. 
2. 
3. 
4. 
5. Home, Add Customer, Add Tariff Plans, Add Tariff Plan to Customer, Pay Billing
6.

title: Add customer/Registration
preconditions:
1. Open https://demo.guru99.com/telecom/addcustomer.php
2. Fill all fields in the form
steps_actions:
1. Press SUBMIT button
2. Check for a Customer ID ( Number of 6 digits), message Please Note Down Your Customer ID, and Home button
3. Press Home button
steps_result:
1. Access Details to Guru99 Telecom page opens
2. Customer ID ( Number of 6 digits), message Please Note Down Your Customer ID, and Home button are present
3. Redirected to the Main page
